OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,7,FHighgate Cemetery in London in the
OL,8,Fface of climate change have been given
OL,9,Fa #6.7 million boost.
OL,11,FThe Friends of Highgate Cemetery
OL,12,FTrust, the charity which owns and
OL,13,Fcares for the resting place of well-
OL,14,Fknown people including Karl Marx,
OL,15,FLucian Freud and George Michael, has
OL,16,Fbeen awarded the grant from the
OL,17,FNational Lottery Heritage Fund.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
