CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779300668
OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FThe grant will contribute to a #19.5
OL,7,Fmillion project to tackle the impacts
OL,8,Fof damage from climate change and ash
OL,9,Fdieback disease, restore neglected
OL,10,Fheritage and increase access and
OL,11,Fcommunity engagement at the cemetery.
OL,13,FThe five-year project is phase one of
OL,14,Fa 25-year "masterplan" to care for the
OL,15,Fheritage-rich and nature-filled site.
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
