OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779300668
OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FOne of the most pressing issues the
OL,7,Fcemetery faces is climate change,
OL,8,Fwhich is bringing increasingly heavy
OL,9,Frainfall in winters and is
OL,10,Fexacerbating years of deferred
OL,11,Fmaintenance by the company that owned
OL,12,Fthe site until 1975.
OL,14,FMuch of the work, such as a new
OL,15,Fdrainage system, will be largely
OL,16,Funseen to the visitors who value its
OL,17,Fromantic, overgrown look as a "place
OL,18,Fapart from the everyday", according to
OL,19,FDr Ian Dungavell, chief executive of
OL,20,Fthe Friends of Highgate Cemetery Trust.
OL,26,@yD@_OUzD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
