PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779300668
OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FHe said: "This grant is a vote of
OL,7,Fconfidence in plans that will preserve
OL,8,Fwhat makes Highgate Cemetery special
OL,9,Fand respect the needs of grave owners,
OL,10,Fwhile opening it up to many more
OL,11,Fpeople."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@HO]
