OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779300668
OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FThe project will improve drainage to
OL,7,Freduce waterlogging from heavy rain
OL,8,Fand capture water for use on the site,
OL,9,Fimprove the condition of paths, remove
OL,10,Fsome trees hit by ash dieback disease
OL,11,Fto open up areas for other plants to
OL,12,Fcome through, and enable new, climate-
OL,13,Fresilient, planting.
OL,15,FThere will also be improvements to the
OL,16,Fcourtyard at the front entrance to the
OL,17,Fcemetery to make it more accessible,
OL,18,Fmore toilets and a new "living room"
OL,19,Fvenue in the Dissenters' Chapel
OL,20,Fopening at the end of the year which
OL,21,Fwill host workshops and displays.
OL,26,@zD@XOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
