OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FConservation work will restore the
OL,7,FGrade I-listed Egyptian Avenue and
OL,8,FCircle of Lebanon, key heritage
OL,9,Ffeatures of the cemetery, including
OL,10,Freinstating one of the obelisks which
OL,11,Fflank the entrance to the avenue.
OL,13,FAnd work to repair the roof of the
OL,14,FGrade II* Terrace Catacombs will allow
OL,15,Fpeople to go up and see the views of
OL,16,FLondon across towards St Paul's
OL,17,FCathedral for the first time in half a
OL,18,Fcentury.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
