CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779300668
OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FThe project, which still needs around
OL,7,F#1 million over five years to meet the
OL,8,F#19.5 million cost, will also work to
OL,9,Fopen up the site in new ways, from
OL,10,Freflective walks for mental health,
OL,11,Fand work experience placements, to
OL,12,Ftelling more stories of the cemetery
OL,13,Fand the 170,000 people buried there,
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
