OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779300668
OL,3,CEfforts to conserve world-famous
OL,4,CHighgate Cemetery get big lottery boost
OL,6,FEilish McGuinness, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe National Lottery Heritage Fund,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This support from National
OL,9,FLottery players will safeguard this
OL,10,Fnationally important, much-loved
OL,11,Fcemetery and its monuments for the
OL,12,Ffuture as well as make it a welcoming
OL,13,Fplace of contemplation and beauty for
OL,14,Fall who visit.
OL,16,F"It will help increase community
OL,17,Finvolvement by offering more learning,
OL,18,Fwellbeing and creative activities and
OL,19,Fan improved visitor experience.
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
